e/Evie_Richards\", \"score\": 0.9999999329950264, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Evie Richards\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evie_Richards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evie_Richards\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 450}, {\"ngram\": \"her bike\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When theformer mountain bike world championcrashed during a World Cup race in Araxa, Brazil in April, she brushed herself off and declared there was \\\"no serious damage\\\", racing again the following day.\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9982862909034097, \"rank\": 0.0015494891452329214, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theformer mountain bike world\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 570}, {\"ngram\": \"a World Cup race\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"Araxa\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 619}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 636}, {\"ngram\": \"no serious damage\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in truth the 27-year-oldhad suffered a concussion- something she would struggle to admit even to herself.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"truth\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"a concussion-\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 793}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think as soon as I crashed, I was like, 'no, I am fine',\\\" Richards told the PA news agency.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 944, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Richards\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 919}, {\"ngram\": \"the PA news agency\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That night, I put on makeup, put on a nice outfit and went down for dinner.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"makeup\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"a nice outfit\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 995}, {\"ngram\": \"dinner\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was like, if I just look fine from the outside no one knows what's going on inside and I can just race.\\\"\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1128, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the outside\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Commonwealth champion had suffered a concussion before while on Grant Ferguson's training camp in the build-up to the 2016Olympics, and knew many of the signs.\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1134, \"end\": 1146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_of_Nations\", \"score\": 0.5729454799307531, \"rank\": 0.4912322586085223, \"text\": \"Commonwealth\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_of_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_of_Nations\"}, {\"begin\": 1198, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulysses_S._Grant\", \"score\": 0.9999999579677032, \"rank\": 4.20271864484058e-08, \"text\": \"Grant\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulysses_S._Grant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulysses_S._Grant\"}, {\"begin\": 1204, \"end\": 1212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferguson_unrest\", \"score\": 0.9999869469101395, \"rank\": 1.262672009040613e-05, \"text\": \"Ferguson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferguson_unrest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferguson_unrest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a concussion\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1181}, {\"ngram\": \"the build-up\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"the signs\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Back then I did not really know it was a concussion but this time I knew,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a concussion\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I also knew the recovery time of concussion and I did not really want to accept it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1470, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the recovery time\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1415}, {\"ngram\": \"concussion\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was no longer possible after Richards had flown home and went for dinner with her family.\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1566, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Richards\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"dinner\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1549}, {\"ngram\": \"her family\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I went for food with my parents and grandparents who I had not seen for a while and mum could see it in my eyes,\\\" Richards said.\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1584}, {\"ngram\": \"my parents\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1600}, {\"ngram\": \"grandparents\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"mum\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1656}, {\"ngram\": \"my eyes\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1680}, {\"ngram\": \"Richards\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1691}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She was like, 'Evie, you are not right'.\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1739, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not even have dinner with my family.\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1784, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dinner\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When your family say you are not right, you need to stop.\\\"\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1843, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your family\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Richards then spoke to British Cycling's medical team and began a proper programme of recovery, returning to racing at the British nationals in early June.\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 2000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1868, \"end\": 1883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\"}, {\"begin\": 1968, \"end\": 1975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9967467830895014, \"rank\": 0.00325875401649947, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Richards\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1853}, {\"ngram\": \"a proper programme\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"recovery\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1939}, {\"ngram\": \"early June\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 1999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the injury behind her, Richards was selected for her second Olympics at the end of June, but the last few months have been a huge learning process for her.\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2162, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the injury\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"Richards\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"her second Olympics\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2075}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2086}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2094}, {\"ngram\": \"the last few months\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2119}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge learning process\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I am always the sort of person who will just 'crack on',\\\" Richards said.\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2245, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sort\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2193}, {\"ngram\": \"person\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2203}, {\"ngram\": \"Richards\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I get that from my dad.\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2270, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my dad\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I wrote in my diary how bad I was (after the crash) and reading it back now, I am like, 'gosh, why did you even race the next day?'\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2406, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my diary\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2294}, {\"ngram\": \"the crash\", \"from\": 2316, \"to\": 2325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even when I raced the next day I did not feel right and did not for the next week.\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2491, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next week\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2490}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I just kept saying, 'oh, maybe it's the impact' and then, 'maybe it's jetlag, maybe I am just tired'.\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2542}, {\"ngram\": \"jetlag\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I was definitely at fault.\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2629, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fault\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2628}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think when there is selection for the Olympics coming, when there is World Cups coming up, it's very hard to step away and take a break, which obviously would have been the best thing to do.\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2822, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"selection\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2661}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2678}, {\"ngram\": \"World Cups\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2711}, {\"ngram\": \"a break\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2767}, {\"ngram\": \"the best thing\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking back, I know a lot more now.\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2861, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If it happens again, I will definitely handle it in a much different way.\\\"\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2936, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a much different way\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Richards will now look forward to her second Olympic appearance.\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 3002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Richards\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 2946}, {\"ngram\": \"her second Olympic appearance\", \"from\": 2972, \"to\": 3001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She finishedseventh on debut in Tokyo, and weeks later stormed to the world title with victory in Val di Sole.\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3035, \"end\": 3040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9802089950698322, \"rank\": 0.01901654535244601, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"debut\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3031}, {\"ngram\": \"weeks\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3051}, {\"ngram\": \"the world title\", \"from\": 3069, \"to\": 3084}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3097}, {\"ngram\": \"Val di Sole\", \"from\": 3101, \"to\": 3112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think anyone who knows me knows I got into sport because of the Olympics, it's all I have ever dreamt of,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3234, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3130}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3166}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think the excitement of being selected ever goes away.\\\"\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the excitement\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since returning to racing, Richards has had a podium finish with fifth place at the Crans-Montana World Cup, coming in sixth in Les Gets last weekend.\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3386, \"end\": 3399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crans-Montana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Crans-Montana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crans-Montana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crans-Montana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"racing\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3327}, {\"ngram\": \"Richards\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3337}, {\"ngram\": \"a podium finish\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3361}, {\"ngram\": \"fifth place\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she will head to Parisstill with many unanswered questions.\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parisstill\", \"from\": 3475, \"to\": 3485}, {\"ngram\": \"many unanswered questions\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am super happy with the podium but I am taking it with a pinch of salt because I have not had the training or the run-up I need,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3519, \"to\": 3661, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 3542, \"to\": 3552}, {\"ngram\": \"a pinch\", \"from\": 3577, \"to\": 3584}, {\"ngram\": \"salt\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3592}, {\"ngram\": \"the training\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3628}, {\"ngram\": \"the run-up\", \"from\": 3632, \"to\": 3642}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not really have any expectations currently on the Games.\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3725, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any expectations\", \"from\": 3685, \"to\": 3701}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3715, \"to\": 3724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just love being a part of it.\", \"from\": 3726, \"to\": 3757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 3744, \"to\": 3750}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd love to medal but I can only get as fit as I can be in the time left.\\\"\", \"from\": 3759, \"to\": 3834, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 3819, \"to\": 3827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PA Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3836, \"to\": 3976, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the page\", \"from\": 3854, \"to\": 3862}, {\"ngram\": \"another page\", \"from\": 3878, \"to\": 3890}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 3894, \"to\": 3902}, {\"ngram\": \"inPlease\", \"from\": 3930, \"to\": 3938}, {\"ngram\": \"your browser\", \"from\": 3947, \"to\": 3959}]}]}"